MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in July rose 7.58% to NT$9,400,408,000 from NT$8,738,052,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  7/2011           7/2010
Sales           9,400,408        8,738,052   
YOY%              7.58%    -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           66,165,286       68,473,424  
YOY%              -3.37% 
=================================================================
 